class app.serializers.WeatherSerializer(*args, **kwargs)

Bases: Serializer

Serializes the Weather program as follows:

  • temperature field is a Float Field, representing current temperature at a location

  • icon field returns the icon to choose to represent the current weather condition

  • condition field returns a description of the current weather

  • surge field gives the multiplier for surge pricing
